    <h1>Landing Page</h1>
    <p class="description">A standalone web page built for one conversion goal — one offer, one CTA, no nav. Well-optimized landing pages convert at <strong>10–25%</strong>, versus 2–5% for general website pages.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
