            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The median conversion rate across industries is approximately 4.3% (Unbounce benchmark). Well-optimized landing pages reach 10-25%. Below 2% usually indicates a headline-offer mismatch, weak social proof, or too many competing CTAs on the page.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">What makes a good landing page?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A strong landing page has one clear offer, a headline that matches the traffic source, minimal or no navigation, compelling social proof above the fold, a single prominent CTA, and a form with as few fields as the offer allows. Message match between the ad and the headline is the highest-impact single factor.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
              <span class="faq-q-text">Do landing pages help SEO?</span>
              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
