            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A homepage introduces the brand to a broad audience with multiple navigation paths and CTAs. A landing page serves one audience segment with one offer and one CTA. Homepages convert at 1-3%; landing pages convert at 4-25% depending on optimization quality.</p></div></div>
          </div>
